text.tspan: Recently, we can found keywords such as eating disorder and bulimia on social media such as YouTube in Korea.
Eating disorders are mostly experienced by people
in their teens and 20s, and I learned that the path
to eating disorders is mostly extreme dieting.
Unlike other services that assist with diet,
Light focuses on overcoming eating disorders.
Light provides an opportunity to adjust ones own diet
based on a meal record function and various challenges,
and provides an opportunity to look back on oneself
